snippet.title: Plants vs. Zombies Game Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for PopCap's next game, Plants vs. Zombies! 
Visit http://www.plantsvszombies.com and be notified of other Zombie Alerts!

It's all because a new PopCap game, Plants vs. Zombies, arrives on May 5. Get ready to soil your plants!
